<H3> <TI>   Germany's MTU Preparing Mach 7 Scramjet </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Germany's MTU Preparing Mach 7 Scramjet </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   94WS0231C Paris AIR &amp; COSMOS/AVIATION MAGAZINE INTERNATIONAL 
in French 7-11 Feb 94 p 22--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> 94WS0231C </F>
<F P=104>  Paris AIR &amp; COSMOS/AVIATION MAGAZINE INTERNATIONAL 
in French 7-11 Feb 94 p 22--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=105> French </F>


