<H3> <TI>   EU To Finance SPOT-4 Satellite Vegetation Instrument </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    EU To Finance SPOT-4 Satellite Vegetation Instrument </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   BR0803122694 Brussels TECH EUROPE in English 4 Feb 94--FOR 
