<H3> <TI>   Italian, French Firms Sign Aerospace Contract </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Italian, French Firms Sign Aerospace Contract </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   MI2502154594 Rome AIR PRESS in Italian 24 Jan 94 p 112--FOR 
