<H3> <TI>   Aerospatiale, BAe, DASA To Cooperate on Concorde Successor </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Aerospatiale, BAe, DASA To Cooperate on Concorde Successor </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   BR0905102194 Paris AFP SCIENCES in French 14 Apr 94 p 12 </F>
