<H3> <TI>   ESA Manned Space Flight Program Adjustments </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    ESA Manned Space Flight Program Adjustments </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   94WS0293D Paris AFP SCIENCES in French 31 Mar 94 p 3 </F>
