<H4>    German Participation in SSTO Vehicle </H4>

<F P=102> 94WS0342B Berlin INGENIEUR DIGEST in German May 94 p 19 </F>
<F P=103> 94WS0342B </F>
<F P=104>  Berlin INGENIEUR DIGEST </F>
