<H3> <TI>   Automated Charging Station to Boost Electric Vehicles </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Automated Charging Station to Boost Electric Vehicles </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   94WS0313A Duesseldorf VDI NACHRICHTEN in German No 14, 8 Apr 
94 p 22 </F>

<F P=103> 94WS0313A </F>
<F P=104>  Duesseldorf VDI NACHRICHTEN </F>
