<H3> <TI>   Aerospatiale Warning to U.K. Government on FTA Program's Fate </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Aerospatiale Warning to U.K. Government on FTA Program's Fate </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   94P60241A Paris LE MONDE in French 11 May 94 p14 </F>
