<H3> <TI>   Eurofighter-2000 Maiden Flight Reported </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Eurofighter-2000 Maiden Flight Reported </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   94P60185A Paris LE MONDE in French 29 Mar 94 p 9 </F>
