<H3> <TI>   France: Defense Minister Declares NH-90 Helicopter Essential </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    France: Defense Minister Declares NH-90 Helicopter Essential </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   94P60185B Paris LE M0NDE in French 25 Mar 94 p 11 </F>
<F P=103> 94P60185B </F>
<F P=104>  Paris LE M0NDE </F>
<F P=105>  French </F>


