<H3> <TI>   Netherlands: Largest Solar Energy Project To Start in </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Netherlands: Largest Solar Energy Project To Start in </PHRASE></F></HT>


<TEXT>
Amsterdam   in 1995 

<F P=102> BR2004141494 Amsterdam POLYTECHNISCH WEEKBLAD in Dutch 14 
Jan 94 p 3 </F>

<F P=103> BR2004141494 </F>
<F P=104>  Amsterdam POLYTECHNISCH WEEKBLAD </F>
