<DOCNO> FBIS4-44762 </DOCNO>
<HT>      "jpest010___94094" </HT>


<HEADER>
<AU>   JPRS-EST-94-010 </AU>
JPRS 
Science &amp; Technology 

</HEADER>

<ABS>  Europe/International </ABS>
<DATE1>   17 March 1994 </DATE1>
<F P=100> WEST EUROPE </F>
<F P=101> TELECOMMUNICATIONS </F>
<H3> <TI>   Germany: 29-32 Billion DM Market Expected in Multimedia </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Germany: 29-32 Billion DM Market Expected in Multimedia </PHRASE></F></HT>


<TEXT>
Area 

