<H3> <TI>   France: Alcatel's Long-Range Plans Presented </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    France: Alcatel's Long-Range Plans Presented </PHRASE></F></HT>
<H4>    Alcatel Optronics </H4>

<F P=102> 94WS0305A Paris L'USINE NOUVELLE in French 31 Mar 94 p 26 </F>
<F P=103> 94WS0305A </F>
