<H3> <TI>   EU Task Forces Pave Way For Trans-European Information </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    EU Task Forces Pave Way For Trans-European Information </PHRASE></F></HT>


<TEXT>
Highway 

<F P=102>   BR0704153094 Brussels EUROTECH FORUM JOURNAL in English Mar 
94 pp 3-4--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> BR0704153094 </F>
<F P=104>  Brussels EUROTECH FORUM JOURNAL </F>
