<H3> <TI>   UK: GKN Group Buys Controlling Share of Westland </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    UK: GKN Group Buys Controlling Share of Westland </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   94WS0314B Paris AIR &amp; COSMOS/AVIATION MAGAZINE INTERNATIONAL 
in French 11-17 Apr 94 p 11--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> 94WS0314B </F>
<F P=104>  Paris AIR &amp; COSMOS/AVIATION MAGAZINE INTERNATIONAL 
