<H3> <TI>   France: EDI Firms Organize To Spur Market </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    France: EDI Firms Organize To Spur Market </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   94WS0325B Paris LE MONDE INFORMATIQUE in French 22 Apr 94 p 
40--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

