<F P=102>   94WS0338A Paris AIR &amp; COSMOS/AVIATION MAGAZINE INTERNATIONAL 
in French 18-24 Apr 94 p 12--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> 94WS0338A </F>
<F P=104>  Paris AIR &amp; COSMOS/AVIATION MAGAZINE INTERNATIONAL 
in French 18-24 Apr 94 p 12--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

