<H3> <TI>   Bull, Ilog Cooperation in Artificial Intelligence Reported </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Bull, Ilog Cooperation in Artificial Intelligence Reported </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   94WS0302B Paris LE MONDE INFORMATIQUE in French 8 Apr 94 p 
6--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

