<H3> <TI>   Italian Defense Industry Restructuring </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Italian Defense Industry Restructuring </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   94WS0314A Paris AIR &amp; COSMOS/AVIATION MAGAZINE INTERNATIONAL 
in French 11-17 Apr 94 p 11--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> 94WS0314A </F>
<F P=104>  Paris AIR &amp; COSMOS/AVIATION MAGAZINE INTERNATIONAL 
in French 11-17 Apr 94 p 11--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

